lico structures, we present our results\nanalyzing small-angle neutron scattering profiles from a solution of core-shell\ntype surfactant coated nanoparticles with varying extents of aggregation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Dec 2022 17:27:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-07"}
