usions: The\nevaluation draws on data and queries from the agroenvironmental domain and\nshows that our source selection method substantially improves the effectiveness\nof federated GeoSPARQL query processing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Dec 2022 18:38:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-07"}
