s\na stronger dependence on averaging of azimuthal angles than the time,\nespecially at high $B_0$ cases. These findings provide insights into the\nanisotropic effect on the estimation of energy transfer rates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Dec 2022 13:14:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-08"}
