AM\nand water above at {\\Sigma} = 6.5 nm-2, the structure of the (OH)2-SAM itself\nat {\\Sigma} = 4.5 nm-2 proposed in this study significantly improves resistance\nto protein adsorption, which provides new insights into the mechanism of\nresistance to protein adsorption on the (OH)2-SAM.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Dec 2022 14:37:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-08"}
