dd $6$-coloring, we improve it by proving that a planar graph without\n$4^{-}$-cycles adjacent to $7^{-}$-cycles has an odd $6$-coloring.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Dec 2022 13:52:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-14"}
